h4. Actor:
Administrator.

h4. Description:
This is the landing page for *Show Task Details* Search Panel on top and "Task" betails at bottom.

h4. Flow: 
* Actor clicks [ARMS|guide:_ShowARMSPlugin] option from top menu bar.
* Disbursement sub menu of left menu should show as default.
* Click "Manage" link from left menu under task .
* [Show landing page for "Manage Task"|guide:_ShowManageTask].
* Enter valid input
* Click on search button
* Show "Task" details

h4. Pre-condition:
* User must have "Show Task Details" privilege.

h4. Process:
* Get specific "Task" details from server.

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** Show "task" details in HTML format at bottom.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].

